            "content": "- This dashboard mimics [VictoriaMetrics Cardinality Explorer in vmui](https://docs.victoriametrics.com/victoriametrics/#cardinality-explorer). In case of problems, it is better to use `vmui` directly.\n- Dashboard requires [Infinity datasource](https://grafana.com/grafana/plugins/yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource/) to be installed and configured to have access to VM: `http://victoriametrics:8428` for vmsingle, `http://vmaselect:8481/select/<tenant>/prometheus` for cluster.\n- Dashboard doesn't use any time filtering: metric usage is tracked globally, and amount of time series per metric is always displayed for **today**.",
